      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a career. that work was my entire framework for understanding the world. without it, the person i was... that person doesn't exist anymore. i look in the mirror and i don't see a scientist, i see a void. it feels like the lights just went out and there's no way to turn them back on.",
